{{Unlicensed}}[[Code Purple]] was a term used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Alliance Intelligence/Legends|intelligence]] [[Division/Legends|division]]. When used in a transmission, it meant that the [[Agent/Legends|agent's]] position had been compromised and [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] entanglements were inevitable.

